	Books    Launch of Sea of Poppies by Amitav Ghosh at Floatel, 9/10 Calcutta Jetty, Strand Road, 6.30pm.    An exhibition of the Penguin Classics Collection at Starmark, Lord Sinha Road, 10.30am to 8pm.    
